</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">Database agent forced off</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><ol>
<li>Investigate whether any events might have forced a database agent off of the remote computer, such as an administrator forcing all users and agents off the remote computer to perform maintenance.</li>

