</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">Database agent terminated</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><ol>
<li>Investigate whether any failures on the remote computer might have terminated a database agent.  For example, the termination of a key database manager process might cause the termination of a database agent.</li>

