<p><strong>sqlstate</strong>:  42611</p>','explanation' => '<p>There is an error in the data type specification in a CREATE or ALTER statement, or a CAST specification. An invalid length, precision or scale attribute may have been specified, or it may be that the data type itself is incorrect or not permitted in this context.  The location of the error is given by <var class="keyword varname">data-item</var> as follows:</p>

