<li>If the same error occurs again, collect the following diagnostic information and troubleshoot the embedded analytics provider: 
<ul>
<li>The values of the parameters of the DB2_SAS_SETTINGS registry variable.</li>

<li>Related information in the db2diag diagnostic log files.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">3</dt>

