</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">16</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>A reference data type or structured data type cannot be used  as a parameter data type or a returns data type of a user-defined function prior to DB2 UDB Version 7.1. Otherwise, a scoped reference  data type or an array data type cannot be used as a parameter data  type or returns data type of a routine. A structured data type or an array data type cannot be used as a return column of a table  or row function.</p>
