<dt class="dlterm">19</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>A default value must be specified when defining a default for a column of a typed table.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">20</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>ALTER TABLE is not supported for a materialized query table.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">21</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>A column cannot be dropped or have its length, data type, security, nullability, or hidden attribute altered on a table that is a base table for a materialized query table.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">22</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>Materialized query tables cannot be defined in a CREATE SCHEMA statement.</p>
