</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">38</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>An index using an index extension is not supported in a multiple partition database partition group prior to DB2 UDB Version 8.1 FixPak 6.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">39</dt>

