</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">52</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The expression of a generated column cannot be modified or added to a column that was not generated using an expression  if that column is a distribution key column or was used in the  ORGANIZE BY clause, the PARTITION BY clause, or the DISTRIBUTE BY clause.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">53</dt>

