</li>
</ol>

<p>For column size limits:</p>

<ol>
<li>Determine the maximum column size for the table that you are trying to create or modify, based on the column type and the underlying page size.</li>

<li>Reduce the length of the affected column so that it does not exceed the limit.</li>
</ol>

