<p>Alternatively, change the rounding mode database configuration parameter (DB config parameter) DECFLT_ROUNDING back to its prior value to avoid all of the potential consequences indicated in this message.</p>

<p>To have the new value for the configuration parameter come into effect, disconnect all applications from this database.  If the database was activated, it must be deactivated.</p>

