<dl>

<dt class="dlterm">1</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>On database servers Version 9.5 and earlier, columns of data type XML are not supported in a table that is organized by dimensions.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">2</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>On database servers Version 9.5 and earlier, columns of data type XML are not supported in a partitioned table.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">3</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>Columns of data type XML cannot be added to a table with existing type-1 indexes. Starting in Version 9.7, type-1 indexes are discontinued and are replaced with type-2 indexes.</p>
