</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">9</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>References to XML data types or values in compound SQL (compiled) statements in functions, triggers, or compound SQL (inlined) statements are not allowed. XML is only supported in compound SQL (compiled) statements in procedures.</p>
