<dt class="dlterm">101</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>Prior to DB2 Version 9.7, the ADD DBPARTITIONNUM  command and the REDISTRIBUTE DATABASE PARTITION GROUP command are not supported on a database partition group that contains tables that have XML columns.</p>
