<p>If starting a new table space rollforward, put the tablespaces into rollforward pending state by restoring them.</p>

<p>If continuing a table space rollforward and one or more of the table spaces involved have been restored and put into rollforward pending state, the table space rollforward in progress must be canceled. Submit the rollforward command again with the CANCEL option and the same table space list. When the rollforward in progress is canceled, the table spaces will have been put into restore pending state. Restore the table spaces and submit the original rollforward command again.</p>

<p>If continuing a table space rollforward and one or more of the  table spaces involved is offline, there are three options:</p>

