<p>This message is returned when the database manager attempts to connect to a remote computer using the TCP/IP communication protocol and receives the error code ECONNREFUSED or WSAECONNREFUSED from the TCP/IP function called CONNECT.  Usually, the connection is refused because the database-related operating system service to which the database manager is attempting to connect on the remote computer is inactive.</p>

