<dt class="dlterm">10</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The REDISTRIBUTE DATABASE PARTITION GROUP command is not allowed  if there are table spaces in the database partition group with tables  having attached partition (SYSCAT.DATAPARTITIONS.STATUS = &#39;A&#39;).</p>
