<dt class="dlterm">11</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The REDISTRIBUTE DATABASE PARTITION GROUP command is not allowed  if there are table spaces in the database partition group with tables  having detached partitions and there are dependent tables that need to be  incrementally maintained with respect to these detached partitions  (SYSCAT.DATAPARTITIONS.STATUS = &#39;D&#39;).</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">12</dt>

