<li>Add the user ID to the group that has CONNECT QUIESCE authority.</li>
</ul>
</li>

<li>In Windows operating system environments: If Extended Security is enabled, add the appropriate user ID to the local Windows security group DB2USERS or DB2ADMNS.</li>
