</li>

<li>Remove any database directory conflicts: 
<ol type="a">
<li>Compare the contents of the local database directory and the system catalog to the database configuration.  In particular, look for the following problems: 
<ul>
<li>Ensure that no two databases have the same name or alias as each other.</li>

<li>Ensure that local database are cataloged as local, and that any remote databases are cataloged as remote.</li>
