<dd class="dlentry"><p>The value of the token <var class="keyword varname">reason-code</var> indicates which special registers would be applied to the new connection:</p>

<ul>
<li>1 or 3: All special register settings up to the point of failure would be returned.</li>

<li>2 or 4: All special register settings (and for DB2 for z/OS Version 10.1.5 and later: session global variables) up to the previous commit point would be replayed on the new connection.</li>
