<p>Scenario 2: If the records in the restart log table have been modified, restore the contents of the restart table.</p>

<p>Scenario 3: If the format of the input files or pipes is not the same as the format of the input files or pipes specified for the original ingest operation, specify input files or pipes that provide the same records and in the same order as on the original ingest operation.</p>

