</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">5</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>Detach data partitions from the source table until there is a single visible data partition using the statement:</p>

<pre class="codeblock"><code>ALTER TABLE ... DETACH PARTITION</code></pre>
<p>Include any necessary set integrity statements.  Otherwise, create a new source table.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">6</dt>

