<dt class="dlterm">9</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>To enable data capture changes on the table that does not have data capture changes turned on, run the statement:</p>

<pre class="codeblock"><code>ALTER TABLE ... DATA CAPTURE CHANGES</code></pre>
<p>To disable data capture changes on the table that does have data capture changes turned on, run the statement:</p>

