<dl>

<dt class="dlterm">1</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>Wait for the log streams to reach the allowed condition, and then retry the takeover operation. An alternative is to use the BY FORCE option of the TAKEOVER HADR command to perform a failover. The BY FORCE option will allow takeover in broader conditions, but may result in data loss and will not change the primary into a standby.</p>
