<dt class="dlterm">2</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>Wait for the log streams to finish local catchup, and then retry the takeover operation.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">3</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>Allow the standby more time to reach the end of the online backup and reissue the command.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">4</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>This command is not supported on a standard or HADR primary database. Issue the command on an HADR standby database only.</p>
