<dl>

<dt class="dlterm">1</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>An unforced takeover (role switch) can be performed only when the HADR standby database is in one of the following states:</p>

<ul>
<li>peer state</li>

<li>remote catchup state with SUPERASYNC mode.</li>

<li>in assisted remote catchup (applicable only in a DB2 pureScale environment)</li>
