</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">2</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The HADR standby database attempted a forced takeover. Forced takeover is not allowed when any log stream is in local catchup state.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">3</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The standby was created from an online backup, and takeover was attempted before the standby had replayed through to the end point of that backup in the log.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">4</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The command was issued against a standard or HADR primary database.</p>
