<dt class="dlterm">5</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The command was issued against an inactive standby database.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">6</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>An error occurred while switching the primary database to a standby database.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">7</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>A communication error occurred during takeover.</p>
</dd>


<dt class="dlterm">8</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The attempted takeover failed because a conflicting command (START HADR, STOP HADR, ACTIVATE DATABASE, or DEACTIVATE DATABASE) or an internal error was encountered on either the primary or the standby database.</p>
