<dt class="dlterm">9</dt>

<dd class="dlentry"><p>The HADR standby database attempted a forced takeover with the PEER WINDOW ONLY command parameter specified.  The takeover failed because the standby database was not in a peer window when it attempted the forced takeover.  Either a peer window is not configured on the standby database, or the forced takeover was attempted outside any peer window that is configured on the standby database.</p>
